{
  "title": "Laced Thai Fish Roast",
  "description": "A salty, crumbly date‑night Thai dish featuring goose fat and a roasted fish fillet glazed with a fragrant lemongrass and lime paste, pescatarian-friendly and perfect for an intimate dinner.",
  "cuisine": "Thai",
